== Introduction ==
OpenDaylight Virtual Tenant Network (VTN) is an application that provides multi-tenant virtual network on OpenDaylight Controllers.

VTN Project plans to develop the VTN system, in which VTN Coordinator orchestrates multiple OpenDaylight Controllers to provide virtual network.

Please see [[OpenDaylight_Virtual_Tenant_Network_(VTN):Main|the Main VTN page]] for more details.

